{"tid":825332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"好文分享【山竹之後，你要知道的.....】","createTime":"2018-09-17T13:20:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-18T01:33:54.000Z","uid":10788,"like":14,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ca2df8f5221d8e7b86c4b2ea97166cf9ecef1625","tid":825332,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:20:33.000Z","msg":"【山竹之後，你要知道的.....】<br />\n我唔係天文台，只係一個普通天文地理愛好者，你可以唔信以下嘅嘢(一切源於全球温室效應强咗)：<br />\n1. 【今次山竹未算勁】今次山竹襲港時，已經唔係 category 5 嘅颱風 (sorry 回歸後我唔用香港天文台嘅料「十號風球」呢D名，亦唔信D風球)，而只係 cat 4，到香港300km時已經開始「散」，亦唔係正面吹正香港，都咁大破壞力，係我見過最强嘅第一個颱風(第2個係温黛），大家諗吓如果 cat 5 正面襲港會點？香港嘅建築物一般可以頂住 250km/hr 陣風幾分鐘幾次，但幾十分鐘呢？【Cat 5 風最少陣風係 &gt;1分鐘及&gt;252km/hr】<br />\n<br />\n2. 以前襲港颱風多生於赤度附近(低緯度)，近菲律賓右邊太平洋，生成一陣就打完菲律賓，再打入南中國海，由於颱風能量源於暖嘅海洋，經過菲律賓再入南海會減弱咗。【但由於全球暖化，生成颱風嘅緯度高咗，D颱風形成後多打去日本台灣】，而強嘅【厄爾尼諾現象出現可以令太平洋中部海水温度升到&gt;26.5℃，有利颱風形成】，今次山竹就係咁，而由於颱風能量源於暖嘅海洋，佢一路行，一路儲能量，山竹最強果陣係285km/hr (遠高於香港建築物抗風標準)，死未？！<br />\n<br />\n3. 【全球暖化，cat 5 颱風陸續有來】，厄爾尼諾幾年一次，全球暖化加厄爾尼諾形成嘅超級颱風會幾年一次，日本人，台灣人，香港人，你哋有心理準備嗎？<br />\n<br />\n4. 【人工島會係颱風中消失】颱風到達時，低氣壓會吸起D海水，今次山竹令海水最高升到4公尺，人工島咪好似將軍澳同杏花村咁囉！今次山竹最近香港果陣氣壓972咋(正常1013)，打菲律賓果陣994，但 cat 5 颱風最低可以 900以下，如果係初二三、十五十六果陣，海水可以升到5-6公尺，尖沙咀地鐵都浸！老老實實，香港未有應付 cat 5 風暴潮嘅經驗囉！<br />\n<br />\n【咁我哋可以做乜？】<br />\n基本上冇乜嘢可以做，用少D電，少碳排放(大6放最多二氧化碳)，少D淘寶，自己個心會安樂D D<br />\n<br />\n祝大家好運，May the Force be with you<br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dr.k.kwong/posts/10156441722845499?__xts__[0]=68.ARCJryyvRXwVlnT6yC3YA6_h7exw8fVPusgHLTbKhEpNZ1LEibhFswApig8kpW7mk66ZQb1-cByQoEGPaVz1Dry6J_LTqeRqq9rXJjTAL5DutiN_qgUVZXTIsh5WkOQHu8glLpHLfeGxzOl8eJNDlQN4rivOBzvJ2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdr.k.kwong%2Fposts%2F10156441722845499%3F__xts__%5B0%5D%3D68.ARCJryyvRXwVlnT6yC3YA6_h7exw8fVPusgHLTbKhEpNZ1LEibhFswApig8kpW7mk66ZQb1-cByQoEGPaVz1Dry6J_LTqeRqq9rXJjTAL5DutiN_qgUVZXTIsh5WkOQHu8glLpHLfeGxzOl8eJNDlQN4rivOBzvJ2&d=8xrTX4oEgcXVd4BAtBD8ADOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=68100971\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dr.k.kwong/posts/10156441722845499?__xts__[0]=68.ARCJryyvRXwVlnT6yC3YA6_h7exw8fVPusgHLTbKhEpNZ1LEibhFswApig8kpW7mk66ZQb1-cByQoEGPaVz1Dry6J_LTqeRqq9rXJjTAL5DutiN_qgUVZXTIsh5WkOQHu8glLpHLfeGxzOl8eJNDlQN4rivOBzvJ2</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />3ToXLffDnQvdKssLOdw&amp;__tn__=C-R[/url]"},{"pid":"edd5405976c02663f0fadfe2eacb40674b501554","tid":825332,"uid":10788,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:22:07.000Z","msg":"香港食正CAT5係遲早既事 好難難次次都咁好彩...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc71bfd9dc07a05671295e5e5d91df2c32e09f5d","tid":825332,"uid":202464,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:23:00.000Z","msg":"要唔要走膠袋？"},{"pid":"ac14df0652a12daeeae99b80db9739cd59bb9f62","tid":825332,"uid":206080,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:25:08.000Z","msg":"全球暖化好似唔係太關事<br />\n<br />\n以前196幾年嘅時候超颱重多過而家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a058c28a983fa7a17c67dabf39e7eef4093707","tid":825332,"uid":28759,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"啫係增加碳排放就可以癱瘓港鐵 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8051aff90585c5ea6e145bc5d0d7d07dd66165e8","tid":825332,"uid":48670,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:34:15.000Z","msg":"支持KFC走飲管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92b3195f0b9fed2c5ffecb887d5852f9c4c8afe8","tid":825332,"uid":14103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-17T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"寫文果位差唔多60歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/o